<h1>Update Pet</h1>
<%=@pet.name%>
<form method='POST' action='/pets/<%=@pet.id%>/edit'>
  <input id="hidden" type="hidden" name="_method" value="patch">

Currently Belongs to Owner Number <%=@owner.id%>, <%=@owner.name%><br/>

You can change Pet Name <br/>
Pet Name: <input type="text" name="pet[name]"><br/>
or Change who this pet belongs to?
  <%Owner.all.each do |owner|%>
<input type="checkbox" name="owner_id" id="<%= owner.id%>" value="<%=owner.id%>"  <%='checked' if owner.id == @owner.id %>></input>
<label for="<%= owner.id%>"><%=owner.name%> </label>
<%end%>





or Add New Owner:


Owner Name:<input type="text" name="owner[name]">
<input type="submit" value="Update Pet">


</form>
